Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:16.31,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,375)} {\bord2}{\fad(200,350)}{\fs24\3c&H0000FF&}1{\3c&H008000&}月{\3c&H0000FF&}5{\3c&H008000&}日是围棋日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:12.45,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一月五日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:13.42,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是围棋日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.34,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:18.00,gogo2,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得去日本棋院参加初下式
